#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.216:7.1"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātaṃ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho, lajjī dayāpanno sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharati. "
msgstr "Take a certain person who gives up killing living creatures. They renounce the rod and the sword. They’re scrupulous and kind, living full of compassion for all living beings. "

msgctxt "an10.216:7.2"
msgid "So na saṃsappati kāyena, na saṃsappati vācāya, na saṃsappati manasā. "
msgstr "They’re not creepy in body, speech, and mind. "

msgctxt "an10.216:7.3"
msgid "Tassa uju kāyakammaṃ hoti, uju vacīkammaṃ, uju manokammaṃ, uju gati, ujupapatti. "
msgstr "Doing virtuous deeds by way of body, speech, and mind, their destiny and rebirth is virtuous. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.216:8.1"
msgid "Ujugatikassa kho panāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ujupapattikassa dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr "Someone whose destiny and rebirth is virtuous is reborn in one of two places, I say: "

msgctxt "an10.216:8.2"
msgid "ye vā ekantasukhā saggā yāni vā pana tāni uccākulāni khattiyamahāsālakulāni vā brāhmaṇamahāsālakulāni vā gahapatimahāsālakulāni vā aḍḍhāni mahaddhanāni mahābhogāni pahūtajātarūparajatāni pahūtavittūpakaraṇāni pahūtadhanadhaññāni. "
msgstr "in a heaven of perfect happiness, or in an eminent well-to-do family of aristocrats, brahmins, or householders—rich, affluent, and wealthy, with lots of gold and silver, lots of property and assets, and lots of money and grain. "

